# OpenFoodFacts Food Product Explorer - Environment Setup

# No environment variables are required for this project
# The OpenFoodFacts API is public and doesn't require authentication

# However, you can optionally set:
# - API_BASE_URL (default: https://world.openfoodfacts.org)
# - NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_NAME (default: FoodFacts)

# For development, this file can be left empty
# All API calls use the public OpenFoodFacts API

# Rate limiting notes:
# OpenFoodFacts API has no strict rate limiting but recommends:
# - Requests per second: Reasonable rate (typically <10/sec)
# - User-Agent: Required for API calls
# - Cache responses when possible

# The app automatically handles:
# - Error responses
# - Network timeouts
# - Missing data gracefully
# - User-friendly error messages
